{"tid":1815843,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府將武漢不明肺炎納入法定須呈報傳染病　今刊憲生效","createTime":"2020-01-07T23:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T00:17:32.000Z","uid":73804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8ea44d07a19021bdd5c613aa95989aaa3fe7a296","tid":1815843,"uid":73804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T23:01:25.000Z","msg":"政府今日刊憲，將涉及武漢不明病毒肺炎的「嚴重新型傳染性病原體呼吸系統病」，納入《預防及控制疾病條例》法定須呈報傳染病，即日生效。<br />\n<br />\n當局可禁止患病人士，及與患者有接觸的人，離開香港。政府會以「先訂立、後審議」的附屬法例形式作出有關修訂。<br />\n<br />\n另外，當局昨日公布，公立醫院再接收多9名病人，他們曾到訪武漢，並出現發燒、呼吸道感染或肺炎徵狀，現時情況穩定，正接受隔離治療。累計數字增至30宗，當中13人已出院。<br />\n<br />\nsource：rthk<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501564-20200108.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501564-20200108.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TdUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=0285d3d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501564-20200108.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4f82ca0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501564-20200108.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"98da19a4f0e7e4f3866c9c51c1c338c30a87337a","tid":1815843,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T23:11:28.000Z","msg":"政府唔係好想香港人死咩，做咩施德政"},{"pid":"68a764195bb38b86253de35dc4d3758d16a5b9d9","tid":1815843,"uid":10056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"98da19a4f0e7e4f3866c9c51c1c338c30a87337a","tid":1815843,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T23:11:28.000Z","msg":"政府唔係好想香港人死咩，做咩施德政"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T23:12:39.000Z","msg":"連個仆街政府都要做野 咁可能真係好撚嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1694c5429df6ac35bafafe418a4013e64ba855","tid":1815843,"uid":113155,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"98da19a4f0e7e4f3866c9c51